1 A HOUSE RESOLUTION honoring those who have
2 served as legislative interns for the Indiana House of
3 Representatives during the Second Regular Session of the 124th
4 Indiana General Assembly.
5 Whereas, The following have served as legislative interns for
6 the Republican Caucus of the Indiana House of Representatives
7 during the Second Regular Session of the 124th Indiana
8 General Assembly: George Andguladze, Isabelle Banet, Dior
9 Chetram, Nala Crumbaugh, Liam Devine, Lia DiPasquale,
10 Jack Dixon, Alexandra Gilbreth, Trinity Jackson, Maxx
11 Johnson, Peter Kaiser, Megan Kath, Casen Lake, Emily Lopes,
12 Jace Magnus, Erika Martin, Griffin McGee, August Miller,
13 Angel Ortiz, Kaylee Prewitt, Isabella Reske, Siena Stefano,
14 Nathaniel Stenseth, Shane Stewart, Sophia Taylor, Ava
15 Tenorio, Stephen Thompson, Stormy Tiede, Jacob Webb, Shawn
16 Wright, and Jackson Ziegler;
20262389
